==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Swiftness
<hw>Swift"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
swift; speed; quickness; celerity; velocity; rapidity; <as>as, the
<ex>swiftness</ex> of a bird; the <ex>swiftness</ex> of a stream;
<ex>swiftness</ex> of descent in a falling body; <ex>swiftness</ex> of
thought, etc.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Swig</ent>⟦br⟧
